headline: 3 Internet Software Stocks to Buy From a Prospering Industry
summary: The Zacks Internet software industry participants like FTNT, ZM and TWLO are benefiting from high demand for SaaS due to the increasing need for hybrid working, learning and diagnosis software, as well as cybersecurity applications.
